<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Yeri's Blog]]></title><description><![CDATA[Yeri's interpretations on various things.]]></description><link>https://yeripratama.com/blog</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Tue, 08 Sep 2020 17:55:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[Custtomizing Vim Lightline]]></title><description><![CDATA[Here’s a summary of how I customize vim lightline plugin to match my needs. The idea is to have statusline that is nice, simple, and still…]]></description><link>https://yeripratama.com/blog/customizing-vim-lightline/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://yeripratama.com/blog/customizing-vim-lightline/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 08 Sep 2020 17:03:22 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;Here’s a summary of how I customize vim lightline plugin to match my needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The idea is to have statusline that is nice, simple, and still useful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So I come up with this setup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Full window, full feature&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/ad00e/full.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;Full&quot;
        title=&quot;Full&quot;
        src=&quot;/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/fcda8/full.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/12f09/full.png 148w,
/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/e4a3f/full.png 295w,
/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/fcda8/full.png 590w,
/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/efc66/full.png 885w,
/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/c83ae/full.png 1180w,
/blog/static/351f23445662287a1bab30efe1830da3/ad00e/full.png 1366w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The left part only have two sections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;&quot; left part&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;mode&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;paste&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;readonly&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;filename&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;modified&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While the right part is simpler with only one section.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;&quot; right part&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;filetype&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;percent&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;lineinfo&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I use &lt;a href=&quot;&quot;&gt;nord&lt;/a&gt; colorscheme, but doesn’t really like the built-in nord theme for lightline, so I customize it to look more subtle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;normal&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;left&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord4&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord3&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;bold&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord4&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord1 &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;normal&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;middle &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord4&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord1 &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;normal&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;right&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord4&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord3 &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the colorscheme file, I define colors extracted from the official nord color pallete, so I don’t need to use the hex value directly.
Each variable is a list containing hex value and their respective value for term color, but I only use terminal with gui colors, so I use default values from built-int nord lightline theme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord0 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#2E3440&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;NONE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord1 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#3B4252&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord2 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#434C5E&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;NONE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord3 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#4C566A&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord4 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#D8DEE9&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;NONE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord5 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#E5E9F0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord6 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#ECEFF4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord7 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#8FBCBB&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord8 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#88C0D0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord9 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#81A1C1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord10 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#5E81AC&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord11 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#BF616A&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord12 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#D08770&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord13 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#EBCB8B&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord14 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#A3BE8C&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord15 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#B48EAD&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;&quot; additional color for accent&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;nord3_bright &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#616E88&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Split window, simplified&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/ad00e/split.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;Split&quot;
        title=&quot;Split&quot;
        src=&quot;/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/fcda8/split.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/12f09/split.png 148w,
/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/e4a3f/split.png 295w,
/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/fcda8/split.png 590w,
/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/efc66/split.png 885w,
/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/c83ae/split.png 1180w,
/blog/static/33d6b12a2c9f61ed07d16a17c7940ee8/ad00e/split.png 1366w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I like the statusline display full path (relative path) for current file, but when using split the space limited, so I adjust the filename to only show the filename. Moreover, I set the lineinfo and filetype component to “dissapear” on specific window width.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The way to do that is by using custom component and bind it to a function we define. For example, this is how I setup the lineinfo component.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; g&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;lightline&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;component_function &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;lineinfo&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;LightlineLineinfo&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;LightlineLineinfo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; abort
